l hosting and collaboration solution.'=>'是知名的雲端商業軟體及服務提供商。Zoho 公司提供電子郵件代管領導品牌 Zoho Mail，以及協同作業解決方案。','is an email infrastructure service offered as an add-on for MailChimp that you can use to send personalized, one-to-one e-commerce emails, or automated transactional emails.You can easily send WordPress emails from your Mandrill account.'=>'是一家電子郵件基礎結構服務提供商，它提供 MailChimp 附加元件，能讓使用者傳送個人化、一對一的電子商務電子郵件或自動化的觸發式電子郵件。網站管理員可以使用自己的 Mandrill 帳號傳送 WordPress 電子郵件。','is a popular transactional email provider that sends more than 35 billion emails every month. If you\'re just starting out, the free plan allows you to send up to 100 emails each day without entering your credit card details.'=>'是一家頗受歡迎、每個月傳送超過 3500 萬封電子郵件的觸發式電子郵件服務提供商。網站管理員可以先使用它的免費方案，不需輸入信用卡資料便能每天傳送 100 封電子郵件。','is a transactional email provider that offers a generous 3-month free trial. After that, it offers a \'Pay As You Grow\' plan that allows you to pay for what you use without committing to a fixed monthly rate.'=>'是一家提供 3 個月免費試用期的觸發式電子郵件服務提供商。試用期過後，使用者可以使用它提供的 [Pay As You Grow] (按需付費) 方案，在不需承諾固定月費率的狀況下，僅為當前的使用量付費。','is one of our recommended mailers. It\'s a transactional email provider with scalable price plans, so it\'s suitable for any size of business.'=>'是其中一個我們推薦的郵件程式。它是具備可彈性調整價格方案的觸發式電子郵件，因此適合不同規模的企業使用。','is a transactional email provider that offers great deliverability and accessible pricing for any business. You can start out with the free trial that allows you to send 100 test emails each month via its secure API.'=>'是一家能為不同規模的企業提供出色的寄達率及合理價格的觸發式電子郵件服務提供商。網站管理員可以先使用它的免費試用方案，透過它提供的安全 API 便能每個月傳送 100 封測試用電子郵件。','is a transactional email provider that\'s trusted by big brands and small businesses. It sends more than 4 trillion emails each year and reports 99.9% uptime. You can get started with the free test account that lets you send up to 500 emails per month.'=>'是一家深受大型品牌及中小企業信任的觸發式電子郵件服務提供商。它每年傳送 4 兆封電子郵件，並維持 99.9% 的運作時間。網站管理員可以先使用它的免費測試帳號，便能每個月傳送 500 封電子郵件。','is a powerful transactional email platform designed to deliver exceptional performance and affordability for businesses of all sizes. which grants you the ability to send 100 test emails every month through our secure API.'=>'是一家能為不同規模的企業提供優秀效能及合理方案價格的觸發式電子郵件平台，並能讓使用者透過它提供的安全 API 便能每個月傳送 100 封測試用電子郵件。','is a leading email service provider that delivers a complete set of email marketing and transactional email solutions.'=>'是一家位居領先地位、提供完整電子郵件行銷及觸發式電子郵件解決方案的電子郵件服務提供商。','a cloud-based email platform was developed by AWS to make sending and receiving emails at scale simple and effective. They also offer tools to create and send out marketing emails.'=>'是由 AWS 開發的雲端電子郵件平台，它能讓大量傳送及接收電子郵件變的簡單有效率。他們也提供可建立及傳送行銷電子郵件的工具。','is a popular transactional email provider that sends more than 35 billion emails every month. If you\'re just starting out, the free plan allows you to send up to 100 emails each day without entering your credit card details'=>'是一家頗受歡迎、每個月傳送超過 350 億封電子郵件的觸發式電子郵件服務提供商。如果網站才剛起步，它的免費方案不需輸入信用卡資料，便能每天傳送最多 100 封電子郵件。','If you\'re just starting out, you can use Brevo\'s free plan to send up to 300 emails a day. You don\'t need to use a credit card to try it out. When you\'re ready, you can upgrade to a higher plan to increase your sending limits.'=>'如果才剛開始使用，使用 Brevo 的免費方案，不需輸入任何信用卡資訊，便能每天傳送最多 300 封電子郵件。當使用量高於免費方案提供的額度時，可以升級至使用量更高的方案以符合需求。','If you are already logged in follow this link to get an'=>'如果已完成登入，請點擊連結以取得',' Follow this link to get the Mailgun'=>'依照這個連結的指示以取得 Mailgun','If you are operating under EU laws then check the above button.'=>'如果網站的營運必須遵守歐盟法律，請點擊上方的按鈕。','Mailjet’s platform enables you to create, send, and track email marketing campaigns, transactional email messages, and email performance metrics.'=>'Mailjet 平台可以讓網站管理員建立、傳送並追蹤電子郵件行銷廣告活動、觸發式電子郵件訊息及電子郵件效能指標。','To use Amazon SES for your wordpress site, you must have an SSL certificate installed on your WordPress site.'=>'如需在 WordPress 網站上使用 Amazon SES，必須先為 WordPress 網站安裝 SSL 憑證。','Please enter Client Secret.'=>'請輸入用戶端密鑰。','Client Se